==English==
===Noun===
'''twig'''
# a small thin [[branch]] of a [[tree]] or [[bush]]

====Translations====
*Dutch: [[twijg]]
*Finnish: [[varpu]]
*French: [[brindille]] ''f''
*German: [[Zweig]] ''m''
*Spanish: [[ramita]] {{f}}
